HTML Code
<article class="col-md-4">
                    <h2>Loops of 7</h2>
                    <p>
                        Using a loop I will be dispalying all the multiples of 7 from 1 - 30 (Ex: 7, 14, 21, etc).
                    </p>
                    <span id="loop-by-seven"></span>
                </article>
                
JavaScript Code
let loopBySeven = document.getElementById('loop-by-seven');

for (var i = 7; i <= 30; i += 7) {
    loopBySeven.innerHTML += i + '<br/>';
}
